The shrine's current location is due to relocation ordered by {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=draft|qq=draft}}’s vassal {{ill|Kuwahara Shigeharu|ja|桑山重晴|qq=draft|qq=draft}} during the {{ill|Tenshō period|ja|天正年間|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Extensive reconstructions occurred in 1596, as evidenced by a {{ill|Ridge Tag|ja|棟札|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, now designated a National Important Cultural Property.

== Cultural Properties ==
