* '''Honden (Main Hall)''': Constructed in 1596, the one-bay {{ill|Nagare-zukuri|ja|流造|qq=draft|qq=draft}} building is designated as a National Important Cultural Property (since December 14, 1931).<ref>{{National Cultural Property Database|102|2822|Kada Kasuga Shrine Main Hall}}</ref><ref>[http://wakayamacity-bunkazai.jp/shitei/784/ Kada Kasuga Shrine, Wakayama City Cultural Properties]</ref>

