'''Kada Kasuga Shrine''' (加太春日神社) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinto shrine|qq=}} located in {{ill|Kada, Wakayama City|ja|和歌山市加太|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kada, Wakayama City|qq=}}, {{ill|Wakayama Prefecture|ja|和歌山県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakayama Prefecture|qq=}}, Japan. It holds historical and cultural significance as a former {{ill|Mura-sha|ja|村社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mura-sha|qq=}}.

== Deities ==
; Primary deities
* {{ill|Ame-no-Koyane|ja|天児屋根命|1=Ame-no-Koyane|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ame-no-Koyane|13=User:Immanuelle/Ame-no-Koyane|qq=}}
* {{ill|Takemikazuchi|ja|武甕槌神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takemikazuchi|qq=}}
* {{ill|Futsunushi|ja|経津主神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Futsunushi|qq=}}

; Additional deities
